  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6605.49 sitting just below the 6609 GEX flip and massive positive gamma walls at 6605 (+49.4B) and 6610 (+52.0B), dealers are currently net long gamma and will sell any rally above 6610 while providing buying support on dips toward 6590. The PIN regime combined with the concentrated positive GEX profile creates a tight trading range, with dealers acting as stabilizers and capping upside momentum. Watch 6610 as the key resistance where dealer selling intensifies, and 6590 as the amplifying negative gamma level that could trigger acceleration if breached.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 6590-6610 with limited directional movement.",
